### Read all users (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users

### Create a new user (MongoDB)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Charlie",
  "role": "admin",
  "email": "charlie3@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Update a user (MongoDB) - replace the id with a real MongoDB ObjectId
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users/replace-with-real-mongo-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Charlie Updated",
  "role": "user"
}

### Delete a user (MongoDB) - replace the id with a real MongoDB ObjectId
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users/replace-with-real-mongo-id
